'''Lìm Hien-Thòng''' ([[Hon-sṳ]]: {{lang|zh|林獻堂}}; [[1881 ngièn]] [[10 ngiet 22 ho]] - [[1956 ngièn]] [[9 ngiet 8 ho]]), miàng '''Chhièu-chhṳ̂m''' ({{lang|zh|朝琛}}), '''Hien-thòng''' he giâ [[pió-jī]], [[ho]] '''Kon-yèn''' ({{lang|zh|灌園}}).

Lìm Hien-thòng chhai [[Tòi-chûng-sṳ]] [[Vu-fûng-khî]] chhút-sâng, he [[Vu-fûng Lìm-kâ]] ({{lang|zh|霧峰林家}}) ke sṳ̀ng-yèn.
